review: Dr. Sonali and her colleagues are very competent in Dental surgery, implants as well as overall mouth rehabilitation. They understood the patient problem very well and advice solution accordingly. They are very friendly in nature and see that patient becomes comfortable in short span of time. Highly recommend to visit Synergy Dental Clinics for Dental issues

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,

review:
Dr Sonali is very friendly *** ********* ******* who patiently understands the concerns and is willing to address them without any qualms.
Dr Bipin and Dr Pallavi ,Owners of Synergy Dental are excellent.They have set up a great place .

Thanks 
Aditi Sheth

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: The Attending Doctor Was Sonali Sasane. I was scared as the attending doctor was new to me and had no previous experience with her. But to my satisfaction she managed to carry out root canal with ease and without any tension to me.  Also thanks to Dr Pallavi for her supervision and guidance.
reply_text: Thanku so much madam for showing faith in me & writing encouraging words for me...

tags: Treatment satisfaction,Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,
review:
All Doctors are really Helpful, have concern about the Patient. Try to understand the basic problems and solve the same with great intregity. 
Dr. Sonali; who treated me is a Hardworking, and always Happy to Help. Her follow up is excellent. I Wish her All the Success in her future Assignments.
reply_text: Thanku very much sir for your kind words...
